SUMMARY:Your Small Business Dream Team: SBA + SBDC Overview
DESCRIPTION:Discover how the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA) and Small Business Development Center (SBDC) work together to support entrepreneurs at every stage of business. Join us on National SBDC Day to learn about funding opportunities\, advising services\, and free resources designed to help you start\, grow\, and succeed.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/your-small-business-dream-team-sba-sbdc-overview/
LOCATION:Zoom Conference
CATEGORIES:Entrepreneurs,Supporting Entrepreneurs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/SBA-SBDC.png
ORGANIZER;CN="WV SBDC":MAILTO:askme@wv.gov
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260318T113000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260318T123000
DTSTAMP:20260313T121314
CREATED:20260309T142401Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T142401Z
UID:10001398-1773833400-1773837000@wvbusinesslink.com
SUMMARY:Planning for a Healthy Business
DESCRIPTION:Spring is around the corner and it’s the ideal time to discover essential planning skills for business success.\nWe’ll focus on the vital role of planning in successful business ownership. Whether participants are just beginning or already on their entrepreneurial journey\, this class inspires them to explore and address essential questions that support building and sustaining a thriving business for the long term. Join the West Virginia District Office of the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA) and the West Virginia Small Business Administration for the series Money Smart for Small Business. This series provides a practical introduction to starting and managing a business that is ideal for both aspiring and established entrepreneurs. The series was developed jointly by the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation (FIDC) and the SBA. Each virtual session comes with a practical workbook guide. Sessions are Wednesdays at 11:30 am beginning March 18\, 2026\, through May 27\, 2026. Register for the sessions that fit your schedule and needs. These sessions will not be recorded.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/planning-for-a-healthy-business/
LOCATION:Microsoft Teams
CATEGORIES:Business Training
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Money-Smart-Planning-eventbrite.png
ORGANIZER;CN="U.S. Small Business Administration":MAILTO:wvinfo@sba.gov
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
