LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T205005Z
UID:10001397-1773928800-1773932400@wvbusinesslink.com
SUMMARY:The Defense Production Act (DPA Title III)
DESCRIPTION:The Defense Production Act (DPA) authorizes the President to ensure availability of certain supplies for defense\, essential civilian\, and homeland security requirements. The DPA Title III provides incentives to develop\, maintain\, modernize\, and expand production capacity and critical technologies. DPA Title III establishes guaranteed loans\, purchase commitments\, grants\, and subsidies to expand production capacity and supplies. DPA Title III helps contractors receive loans\, direct investments\, purchase commitments and other assistance to help in bolstering the supply chain. We will provide you with a full overview of DPA Title III programs and resources as a small business contractor. \nThis APEX Accelerator is funded in part through a cooperative agreement with the Department of Defense.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/the-defense-production-act-dpa-title-iii/
LOCATION:Zoom Webinar
CATEGORIES:Government,Sales/Procurement,Webinar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/New-RCAC-APEX-Logo-5-15-24.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="RCAC APEX Accelerator":MAILTO:kpriddy@rcacwv.com
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260324T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260324T130000
