LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T141345Z
UID:10001394-1774353600-1774357200@wvbusinesslink.com
SUMMARY:Utilizing E-Tools
DESCRIPTION:The General Services Administration (GSA) offers a suite of integrated e-tools to make the acquisition process more efficient for small businesses. These complimentary e-tools help you perform market research\, locate contracting opportunities\, and more. Join the GSA Office of Small and Disadvantaged Business Utilization (OSDBU) and the West Virginia Apex Accelerator as they team to introduce GSA’s e-tools and methods for your business to gain an advantage in achieving acquisition efficiency. \nThis APEX Accelerator is funded in part through a cooperative agreement with the Department of Defense.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/utilizing-e-tools/
LOCATION:Zoom Webinar
CATEGORIES:Government,Sales/Procurement,Webinar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/New-RCAC-APEX-Logo-5-15-24-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="RCAC APEX Accelerator":MAILTO:kpriddy@rcacwv.com
END:VEVENT
