SUMMARY:Bridging Innovation Week 2026
DESCRIPTION:[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=”” css_params=””]Bridging Innovation Week is the state’s premier ​entrepreneurship event. The annual symposium ​advances entrepreneurship-led economic ​development by providing connection and education ​to business owners\, current and prospective ​entrepreneurs\, and entrepreneur serving ​organizations (ESOs) throughout West Virginia. \nWhether you’re just starting or looking to scale\, this is ​the place to explore entrepreneurship opportunities ​in the Mountain State! Join us in Morgantown\, WV on April 27 – May 1\, 2026. To learn more or to register for Bridging Innovation Week 2026 visit https://www.wveshipecosystem.com.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/bridging-innovation-week-2026/
CATEGORIES:Bridging Innovation,Conference,Entrepreneur Competitions,entrepreneur education,Entrepreneurs,Pitch Competition
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/bridging-innovation-logo-black.png
ORGANIZER;CN="West Virginia Entrepreneurship Ecosystem":MAILTO:connect@wveshipecosystem.org
END:VEVENT
